Juvenile dark morph.description: Immature Heermann's Gulls are sometimes mistaken for Jaegers, but Parasitic Jaegers have longer pointer wings with white flashes under the wing.

Immature dark morph.description: Pomarine Jaegers are dark like immature Heermann's Gulls, but they have pointer wings and white flashes under the wing that Heermann's Gulls don't have.
